sql:
SELECT SUM(duration_watched) AS total_duration_watched
FROM watch_history
WHERE video_id = '1';

SELECT SUM(view_count) AS total_views
FROM video_metrics
WHERE video_id = '1';

external_knowledge:
- "most watched" refers to the highest view count; 
- "most engaging" refers to the highest engagement score; 
- "widely viewed" refers to the highest number of unique watchers.

sql:
SELECT video_id
FROM video_metrics
WHERE engagement_score > 0.7;
